1. A system with Docker installed.  
2. Minimum 8GB RAM for smooth container performance.  
3. Stable internet connection for image pulls and package installations.

## Software Requirements: {#software-requirements:}

1. Docker and Docker Compose.  
2. Visual Studio Code with Playwright extension.  
3. Node.js and NPM for JavaScript test automation.

## Network Requirements: {#network-requirements:}

1. Open ports for Docker containers.  
2. Localhost access on port 3000\.  
3. External web access for Open Letter Opener.
